{"tid":1504751,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"何韻詩助視障人士離示威區","createTime":"2019-08-25T11:34:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-25T12:55:03.000Z","uid":25558,"like":14,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"4f990027a241f5c972a33be284d5135c924fcf57","tid":1504751,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T11:34:22.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/entertainment/daily/article/20190825/20755409\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190825%2F20755409&d=6v%2BmLhPCoO19KIzpXGl1Drc9MeEcP%2Bid7GYOBZmoUoI%3D&h=824e8922\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190825%2F20755409&h=ab728ebc\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/entertainment/daily/article/20190825/20755409</a><br />\n<br />\n何韻詩助視障人士離示威區<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20190825/large/1566656560_d7d1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20190825%2Flarge%2F1566656560_d7d1.jpg&h=e4f2b1ba&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n阿詩沿路拖着該視障人士，協助她離開警方驅散範圍。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n觀塘遊行昨日結束後，大批示威者集結在偉業街，警方隨後施放催淚彈驅散，情況非常混亂，何韻詩昨日也有參與觀塘遊行，還在fb開live直擊。阿詩一直在牛頭角警署對面，從高處直擊現場情況，見到有人被捕，她發出「唉」聲說：「再放催淚彈喇，好，我諗緊係咪可以行落去&hellip;&hellip;我係咪應該落去呢？其實呢邊係有一堆防暴頂住條路，其實兩邊都係有&hellip;&hellip;等我思考吓應該去邊邊行，等我off一off先，我行咗再話畀大家聽。」<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：汪明荃主張和平<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20190825/large/1566656560_c733.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20190825%2Flarge%2F1566656560_c733.jpg&h=99df8ffb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n貼心的阿詩還蹲下為視障人士綁鞋帶。互聯網圖片<br />\n<br />\n阿詩在下午約4時40分終止直播，《蘋果》也有聯絡何韻詩，但未獲回覆。阿詩隨後再開live，她解釋：「我哋頭先喺工業大廈度俾人圍住，警察態度惡劣，叫我哋落去又唔畀我哋落去，我哋頭先係被困嘅。」直播期間，她還拖着一位女視障人士離警方驅散範圍，但一路找不到離開方向，她形容：「好似荒島一樣。」阿詩指曾向警方查詢如何讓視障人士離開，但遭警方呼喝。<br />\n<br />\n撰文：翁可人 <br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n金義聖鬧爆香港警察<br />\n<br />\n汪明荃主張和平<br />\n阮民安：唔犯法都會支持<br />\n楊千嬅新劇獲無綫放行<br />\n金義聖鬧爆香港警察<br />\n影公司反罷工通告遭秋後算賬TVB被炒員工控訴白色恐怖"},{"pid":"b0476e857ac6f8fd1aca3cff5b93152f18d13cd5","tid":1504751,"uid":76632,"like":13,"dislike":1,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T11:43:30.000Z","msg":"梅姐最有價值嘅遺產之一<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6715f1fc2ee8c05ed6a7f55f3f72ccc12443f840","tid":1504751,"uid":176114,"like":2,"dislike":5,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"b0476e857ac6f8fd1aca3cff5b93152f18d13cd5","tid":1504751,"uid":76632,"like":13,"dislike":1,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T11:43:30.000Z","msg":"梅姐最有價值嘅遺產之一<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T11:56:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 講野之前經下大腦<br />\nhocc係asset？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"469fb8b0592b78283c7d95ab602deb8557d91125","tid":1504751,"uid":76632,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6715f1fc2ee8c05ed6a7f55f3f72ccc12443f840","tid":1504751,"uid":176114,"like":2,"dislike":5,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"b0476e857ac6f8fd1aca3cff5b93152f18d13cd5","tid":1504751,"uid":76632,"like":13,"dislike":1,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T11:43:30.000Z","msg":"梅姐最有價值嘅遺產之一<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T11:56:5